      ],
      "coachingCues": [
        "The 'dead leg' barely touches the ground — like stepping on hot lava",
        "Dip your shoulder on the dead leg side — sell it with your upper body",
        "Keep your speed — this move works because you DON'T slow down much",
        "Think 'soft step, hard step' — soft right, then HARD left",
        "Eyes glance right during the drop, snap forward-left when you go"
      ],
      "commonMistakes": [
        "Putting too much weight on the dead leg (defeats the purpose — it should be feather-light)",
        "Over-exaggerating the dip (takes too long, defender recovers)",
        "Stopping forward momentum during the drop (should barely decelerate)",
        "Forgetting the shoulder dip (the leg alone isn't enough to sell it)",
        "Dead leg stepping too far out (makes recovery step too long)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "get-skinny",
      "name": "Get Skinny",
      "description": "Turn your body sideways to slip past a defender in tight space. No fake — just reduce your profile and slide through the gap. Essential for 5v5 where space is limited.",
